    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the night at the museum</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this first-person experience, the museum has long been safeguarded by an ancient, mighty Viking artifact, warding off evil spirits for centuries. However, a powerful, dark entity has recently emerged from the shadows, capturing the artifact and shattering the museum's protective seal. This sudden disturbance has caused supernatural chaos, making it a deadly place for any living being. You, as a janitor, find yourself caught in the middle of all this while it's happening.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Clean</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for some <strong>next-level, never-before-seen cleaning action!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/2d8369ab350e28b31766a21c897b668f.poster.avif?t=1754082171\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/2d8369ab350e28b31766a21c897b668f.webm?t=1754082171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/2d8369ab350e28b31766a21c897b668f.mp4?t=1754082171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the museum's hidden history room by room. Each exhibit holds secrets waiting to be solved.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/e67de0aed2d80d1498252a9190d699f8.poster.avif?t=1754082171\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/e67de0aed2d80d1498252a9190d699f8.webm?t=1754082171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/e67de0aed2d80d1498252a9190d699f8.mp4?t=1754082171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're not alone on this night shift. Strange things stir in the shadows, and the museum's past isn't as quiet as it seems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/1adfaf4bce6e48a23fb482f6d6b48603.poster.avif?t=1754082171\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/1adfaf4bce6e48a23fb482f6d6b48603.webm?t=1754082171\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3234290/extras/1adfaf4bce6e48a23fb482f6d6b48603.mp4?t=1754082171\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
